lines.text: Hey Terminator... I don't know where you came from, but you better go back.
[grabbing Yung by the neck]
I really want to kill you, but you're not worth it.
Everybody knows Yung killed Kim, dick...
[Jeff cuts him off with a harsh glare]

[finishing]
... Tracy.

[after beating three guys]
Where is he?
Forget it.

[locking his arm]
We had a deal. Talk.
Croc-pit.
Where?
Croc-pit Club. He hangs out there. They all do.
Thanks. Who said it never hurt to ask?
I wonder if I could kick your ass... Wait... not just you... all three of you.
When you get him, kill for Kim. Kill for me.
I have shown you the way of the dragon, but you have not seen it. Experience will be your teacher.
I wonder if I could kick your ass. No, not just you. All three of you.
Are you serious?
Yeah. Are you? I take on all three of you, you point me in the right direction. Deal?
Full contact. No protection.
No problem.
